name: Multiverse_
description:
The game is about a physicist who finds herself in a different universe and tries to travel back to the milky way in order to do that she has to fight aliens and different creatures

How to play:
  Jump, press space
  Fight press, x
  Run press, shift
  Show ID, press i

All models made with Blender
